queue

public void queue(BatchRequest batch,
                  JsonBatchCallback<Search> callback)
           throws IOException
Queues the "list" request to the Customsearch server into the given batch request.

Example usage: 

         request.queue(batchRequest, new JsonBatchCallback<Search>() {

           public void onSuccess(Search content, GoogleHeaders responseHeaders) {
             log("Success");
           }

           public void onFailure(GoogleJsonError e, GoogleHeaders responseHeaders) {
             log(e.getMessage());
           }
         });

Parameters:
batch - a single batch of requests
callback - batch callback
Throws:
IOException

1.6
